summary: This appears to be an FBI 302 form (report of investigation) from the New York Field Office's Violent Crimes Task Force, referencing the Epstein case. The document is an email transmitting the finalized report, indicating it contains investigative findings or interview summaries.

events.title: Finalized FBI 302 Report Transmitted
events.description: A finalized FBI 302 report from the New York Field Office's Violent Crimes Task Force was transmitted via email regarding the Epstein case.

keyFacts: The document is an FBI 302 report from the New York Field Office's Violent Crimes Task Force.
It was finalized and transmitted via email on September 18, 2019.
The report is related to the Epstein investigation, as indicated by the file reference EFTA00017783.
The email was copied to the Office of the Inspector General (OIG).
